title: John Lee Hooker - 40th Anniversary Album (1989) [FLAC]
description:
released 1989, contains previously unreleased recordings from 1948 to 1961

The Hook on acoustic and electric guitar, sometimes solo (with characteristical foot-stomping), sometimes with support


John Lee Hooker - vocals, guitar
Sylvester Cotton - guitar
Andrew Dunham - guitar
Eddie Burns - guitar, harp
Bernie Besman - piano, organ
